{"tid":2086303,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【天譴】又有境外蝗蟲大軍或將入侵中国","createTime":"2020-06-30T08:42:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T10:50:49.000Z","uid":293677,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3931e4def275ca2b65fb2dca3f78ddd142ab4e9c","tid":2086303,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:42:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3212927\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3212927&d=r9GgQvVcrWtMp%2Fshn5VX%2FxURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=afcea89c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3212927&h=5c845d92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3212927</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/06/30/php9vWxA2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F06%2F30%2Fphp9vWxA2.jpg&h=279e623f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2020-06-30 13:25:18<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕尼泊爾農業和畜牧發展部發言人（Hari Bahadur KC）在27日表示，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">尼泊爾南部平原已發現蝗蟲蹤跡，他們懷疑蝗蟲是由印度吹來的不穩定氣流入境。尼泊爾罕見爆發蝗災，也令外界擔憂是否沙漠蝗蟲又多一條侵入中國的「新路徑」。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n由於尼泊爾地理位置和氣候條件特殊，蝗災在該國並不常見。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">目前在中東、南亞地區爆發的是第二波蝗災，規模是第一波的20倍</span></span>。此前，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中國農業科學院植物保護研究所研究員張澤華曾表示，<ins>第二波蝗蟲入侵中國的可能性很高</ins>。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n其他專家也曾預測，若氣候條件適宜，沙漠蝗蟲入境中國有3種路線，一是從巴基斯坦和印度直接進入西藏；二是從經緬甸進入雲南，三是經哈薩克斯坦進入新疆。但中國均未預測從尼泊爾入境的可能性，「蟲蟲大軍」入侵中國可能的路徑再增加。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">熱烈歡迎蝗蟲大軍武統中国</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h66ZvWX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh66ZvWX.jpg&h=47043062&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a07b4f43216b24d491cfc9065eab6f84c1c5c12","tid":2086303,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:43:20.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GpmR6vJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGpmR6vJ.png&h=7e850275&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"d155b3e3cb8d6d2d042973360601cab09f1594e4","tid":2086303,"uid":69746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:43:48.000Z","msg":"回鄉探親罷了 沒事兒 沒事兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47867a1c85f191c766c7abf6152be6d609d6c3ef","tid":2086303,"uid":333381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:43:52.000Z","msg":"團聚了，感動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55e38d1c80522f36715325baa1b16735f55bbdc3","tid":2086303,"uid":207792,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:45:15.000Z","msg":"到左先算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上次夠話非洲蝗去緊啦"},{"pid":"1f51982a22713051db20388a64e82e8f3cbe0eae","tid":2086303,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55e38d1c80522f36715325baa1b16735f55bbdc3","tid":2086303,"uid":207792,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:45:15.000Z","msg":"到左先算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上次夠話非洲蝗去緊啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:46:35.000Z","msg":"今次係第二波<br />\n多左20倍<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69f06e614a5e8f25ddd5f6a6b497926ad0de22aa","tid":2086303,"uid":227929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:47:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>7.1不見不散</strong></span></span><img src=\"https://na.